document.full_text: the international criminal court prosecutor said on wednesday he will request arrest warrants for the killing of pro-democracy demonstrators in libya, and u.n. envoys said one target could be libyan leader muammar gaddafi.
document.title: icc prosecutor seeks 3 arrest warrants on libya
